= Presentations

== Guidelines for Presenting

=== Barry Arthur


=== Preparation

* Use Your Own Words
* Have an Outline
* 15 Word Summary
* Practice, Practice, Practice


=== Slides

* 10 / 20 / 30 Rule
* 20 / 20 Rule
* DON'T Read
* Few Words


=== Slides

* Colour Carefully
* Pictures are Good
* *Appropriate* Pictures are Good
* NO Transitions


=== Delivery

* Slow Down
* Make Eye Contact
* Breathe In

